headline.main: Even Tesla Seems Worried It’s Consuming Too Much Cash: DealBook Briefing

headline.main: F.B.I.’s Urgent Request: Reboot Your Router to Stop Russia-Linked Malware

headline.main: The Next Privacy Battle in Europe Is Over This New Law
headline.print_headline: In Europe, New Battle On Privacy

lead_paragraph: The tech industry is fighting a pending measure that’s even stricter than the recently enacted G.D.P.R. It’s called the ePrivacy Regulation.
